name: Crimson Chinatown
description: Collaboration project between Lucius Felimus and Angela Clarisse Chua, depicting a Chinatown in a cyberpunk megalopolis. Procedurally generated using cell noise displacement textures on different meshes of geometry with added architectural features, holograms, neon signs, traffic, and atmospheric effects. Rendered in Blender Eevee. Featured OBJKT: #243180 "The Automaton's Reverie" by @JarrettPinto.
